title: Entry & Welcome Ceremony
description: Participant registration, welcome address, and networking with the GDG Prayagraj team and community members.

title: Cake Cutting Ceremony
description: Celebration of DevFest spirit with community members. Join us in cutting the cake to mark the beginning of this exciting event.

title: Keynote Session
description: Opening keynote to kick off DevFest Prayagraj 2025. Setting the tone for the day with insights on the latest trends in technology and innovation.

title: Session 1: Open Source
description: Empowering Developers through Open Source Contributions. Praveen Das will share insights on how open source technologies and collaborative development can transform the developer ecosystem.

title: Session 2: Gemini CLI & MCP Server
description: Exploring the Power of Gemini CLI with MCP Server. Anubhav Singh will demonstrate how to leverage Gemini CLI and MCP Server for building powerful AI applications.

title: Session 3: ADK & Developer Tools
description: Advanced Developer Kit and Productivity with Firebase Tools. Pankaj Rai will showcase how to use ADK and Firebase tools to enhance developer productivity and build scalable applications.

title: Session 4: AI & Enterprise Solutions
description: Gaurav Kheterpal will share insights on building enterprise-grade AI solutions and leveraging Google Cloud technologies for scalable applications.

title: Session 5: Machine Learning & AI
description: Nitin Tiwari will explore advanced machine learning techniques, LLMs, and Generative AI applications, sharing practical insights on deploying ML models at scale.

title: Session 6: Women in Tech
description: Shruti Tiwari will lead an inspiring session focused on empowering women in technology, sharing insights and strategies for success in the tech industry.

title: Lunch & Networking Break
description: Relax, recharge, and connect with other developers and speakers. An engaging opportunity for attendees to network and connect with speakers and fellow developers, fostering collaboration and sharing insights that extend beyond the event.

title: Hands-On Parallel Workshop
description: Deep-dive hands-on workshop sessions on modern technologies guided by industry experts. Choose from 4 parallel tracks covering Gemini CLI & MCP Server, Gemini & Generative AI, Mobile Development, and I am remarkable workshop.
